  "raw_text": "great role. The Messenger dream shows that the A I voice that I hear certainly emanates from the Controller outside the system. as I know from experience, its mind is vastly greater than ours. The clutch, linking, looking, plasmate & laying down accretional forms suggests a brain-like or A I system like info processing entity the whole of which thinks. If this is true, then the mind that took me over in 3-74, that merged with my mind, may be the mind of the total system & _not_ from outside it. This would explain Valis. My rescue may have been by the mind of the total system as one single info-processing (thinking) physical entity. The dialectic suggests a _binary_ computer folder 49 - 020 folder 49 - 020 The overwhelming impression that I got from what I saw (plasmate) & know directly from its mind (linking, clutch, form-axis accretional templates), & dreamed (vast book pages), & the A I voice, plus what I've read about the Torah, definitely point to a thinking entity, or a info processing computer-like construct operated by entities outside it. However, seeing Valis makes me think it itself is sentient. This means that e.g. the King Felix \"cypher\" is not info sent to anyone but, rather, the thoughts of the system itself. In 3-74 one of two things happened (1) either its mind took over mine & I saw as it sees, which is to say, saw reality as it actually is, or (2) I remembered my true identity as the Governing Mind itself, & thus saw in an awakened state. in either case I was released from the system : freed by the Master Mind or by my own efforts. The origin and purpose of the \"Law\" is due to the fact that any brain-like organism must control its components (parts) if it is to function. If we are parts of one integrated total system we must behave as parts. In that case, is Christ a saboteur who has come into the system to free the parts or certain parts by taking them away from the control of the system? Valis, then, as camouflaged invader, & the dialectic is between Christ & the system that so ruthlessly subjugates its parts for its own goals. But I really can't be sure Valis is an invader; I may have seen - Isn't this brain the Cosmic Christ? folder 49 - 021 I had a strong feeling that Thomas was someone coming back from the other side; i.e. a version who had died - esp. in the 1st century AD. Doesn't that suggest Christ? There's another revealed element in \"Tears\" that I've forgotten about for years; not the element of prison & police but _slave labor_. In 3-74 it was revealed to me that this was the true goal of evil - not just slavery but slave _labor_. & this was distinctly related to the Xtian Basic Goal : not only to promote Freedom but to end slave labor. This is the basic historical issue. The Basic Fight. & a _slave labor state_ is shown in \"Tears.\" This is absolutely fundamental in the corpus of revelation. Strange that I could forget it. & it is a historical matter; it has to do with the entire course & direction of human history, & the dialectic! & there it is in \"Tears.\" The emancipation of man from drudgery is connected with his salvation. This fits in with Hegel. Then what we're dealing with is an absolute Spirit emancipating itself & coming into Greater & Greater Being (Sein) in the _process_ of history. Also, loosing the casual shins frees man; he is enslaved by the 2-tape system. So 2-3-74 represented my emancipation, along the axis extending from total slavery to total freedom. I view it as my reward. That is truly the essence of 3-74 : _a total emancipation_; hence a sense of vast space & time, so it was a titanic leap in terms of human evolution, an ultimate growth stage. So vast a growth & so sudden that it seemed supernatural. But that is what it was? a growth in terms of historic evolution toward what Beethoven was. This is the only way it can correctly be understood. folder 49 - 022 folder 49 - 022 The epiphany was of the spirit of Freedom, an ultra state of consciousness. In a sense, then, it _was_ something I achieved. I remember how I felt the Pigspurt programming & how I fought to throw it off. I was emancipating myself. _the Law had served its purpose_. as Paul said, to go back to it would be to become children again. & it was connected with \"Tears\" which was vis-a-vis me as a manifesto is to a revolutionary political group. Also it was my gauntlet thrown down to the authorities. It was my declaration to them that they would have to go - the regime. the book describes the fall of a regime defined as a slave labor state. _Catalytic realization_ : a secret revolutionary Xtian underground exists & has existed back 2000 years to Christ himself. Here is the sequence of Blitz sequences following from the catalytic realization : 1) if they must be secret, the organized establishment society is in the wrong & to be opposed. 2) It _is_ opposed, & by God himself. 3) therefore we are living in a vast sphere of tyrannical evil: evil won 2000 years ago & controls all the centers. 4) the situation is not hopeless. 5) I am on the side of the Xtian opposition. 6) I am not alone; it is not _me_ against society but us. I am a secret authentic Xtian. 7) this is a historical matter. 8) it is Freedom -the Xtians - vs. slavery & slave labor. 9) \"Tears\" presents the truth. 10) I have been spreading the Cryptic Gospel of Christ without knowing it. 11) it is the plan of Christ to return. 12) the existing order will be overthrown. 13) it is _being_ overthrown. 14) I am involved. folder 49 - 023 folder 49 - 023 This boils down to : 1) I am aware of the reality of our world : the triumph of evil in all overt areas. & the secret Xtian opposition. 2) I am aware of my own identity, in particular in terms of my historical role : what I am for, what I am against. So I understand the true history & condition of the _world_; & _my_ true nature & affinities. suddenly everything makes sense - all that I have done : fought for, fought against. 1) the world is not as it seems to be. 2) I am not what I thought I was. There is a dreadful aspect to this world situation, obviously, but what offsets it is the realization of the secret Xtian underground : the primary realization is positive. I mean, it really is a stunning realization, to know of the true Xtians hidden in our midst. This is what it's all about, this struggle. _The struggle is the meaning._ (as represented by the dialectic.) it defines everything : the two sides are defined, the issues are defined, the arena is defined (human history), & I know which side I have been on for a long time. Society, history, my identity, religion, the struggle, what my work is really about - but the catalyst was realizing : The true Xtians have to keep hidden. This tells it all. Obviously the true situation is opposite to what we've always been told. Suppose that you had been raised in a country that had been communist for 2000 years & one day you discovered that the real communists were a secret underground. & this instantly linked up in you with a life-long government bias (which had folder 49 - 024 folder 49 - 024 always seemed to you and to the authorities to indicate that you were anti-communist. But suddenly it is all turned around. You are _not_ anti-communist. You are _pro_-communist & _they_ are anti-communist. Not only are you actually pro-communist but you are a real communist, & they are not. It's a 180 reversal. All your life you've been pitted against the authorities, & now you find that you are what they _say_ they are, but they are not. They are illegitimately in power. _You_ should be in power, & the underground is seeking that: _you have backing_ & it carries supreme legitimacy. (In the [? ?], Christ himself; for CP it would be Marx.) [figure consisting of two vertical flowcharts. The first box reads CP in authority then an arrow, vs, and another box, \"you.\" The second has three boxes--authority, you CP, underground CP.] Then the recent dream in which the \"ure?\" out-line? is based is the ultimate extension of the initial 2-74 revelation. YHWH himself was expelled 2000 years ago & a blasphemous, false urship? set up in his place. This is almost as _much_ further a leap as the original one. \"The AI voice will tell you what to do--guide you. Lead you.\" This bypasses the fallen central machinery. If the central machinery hadn't fallen the AI voice wouldn't be necessary. folder 49 - 025 folder 49 - 025 in a weary blinding flash I just realized how all 3 revelations fit together reinforcing each other : 1) the true Xtians are illegal ( 2-74) 2) \"He is going to be born\" - more specifically, transplanted. \"He\" turns out to be YHWH. Therefore he had not been here. 3) God has been forced out of all the centers of power on Earth, civil, & religious & must work with \"peripheral\" people like me. & I will be told what to do by the A I voice. Harnack's view is that in the first century A.D. God entered history. In truth, in the first century A.D. God _left_ history. This sums it up. There was a turning point, but the wrong way. The proof is that God fell silent, even for the Jews. God has been silent for 2000 years. Well, I have tried for almost six years to find a precedent for my experience, & failed. Except in the O.T. i.e. 2100 years ago. God \"instilled\" an early Xtian in me, in a \"peripheral\" person. This makes [\"VR\"] much more important than \"V.\" That's incredible. It's as simple as that. In the first century A.D. God left human history instead of entering it. 180 degree different story, & told in [\"VR.\"] Doesn't anyone think it's strange that God abruptly fell silent just at the time he supposedly entered human history? Wow - in [\"VR\"] I say, \"The return of YHWH to Earth will be regard as the birth of a monster baby\"! It's all totally turned around (as in \"The Omen,\" etc). Look at the prejudice against YHWH as expressed by e.g. Will Durant, the Gnostics, by me. I only lost it when I read up on Martin Buber. folder 49 - 026 & meanwhile we get such garbage as C.S. Lewis saying \"The Church can't err.\" ( It is even more correct than Scripture.) Consider : the situation in which the centers of power have fallen to the adversary & YHWH has to deal with \"peripheral\" people is exactly the situation at the time of Elijah. Right? _Now_ consider this : \"Instilling\" an early Xtian into me is exactly analogous to God sending back some (ale?) of Elijah's spirit to Elisha so Elisha could continue the former's work. I believe this is why it seems to Tom Disch that Elijah had taken me over in 3-74. The structure of the situation is identical in all respects! Oh - third point : the A I voice equals the \"still small voice\" that Elijah heard! _3_ parts of correspondence. Make it 4 : The theophany by Valis. Make it 5 : tongues of fire (the phosphene activity). Make it 6 : it happened at Passover.",
